        "content": "<p>Hi, and welcome! The <code>intro</code> tactic is supposed to be used on a goal of the form <code>p -&gt; q</code>, to introduce the hypothesis <code>p</code>. But here your hypotheses are already introduced (they are <code>x</code>, <code>y</code> and <code>hx</code>), so <code>intro</code> has nothing to introduce.</p>",
